## **PHASE 7: MACRO OVERLAY & REGIME DETECTION**
*"Adapt strategy to market environment"*

### **Four Market Regimes**

```
REGIME CLASSIFICATION FRAMEWORK:

REGIME 1 - RISK-ON (Goldilocks):
Indicators:
â”œâ”€ VIX-equivalent <15
â”œâ”€ Credit spreads tight (<200bp)
â”œâ”€ IDX making new highs or strong uptrend
â”œâ”€ Foreign flows: Net buying
â”œâ”€ Earnings beats > misses
â””â”€ Sentiment: Greed, complacency

Strategy:
â”œâ”€ Equity allocation: 70-80% (fully invested)
â”œâ”€ Sector preference: Growth, cyclicals, small caps
â”œâ”€ Leverage: Can use moderate leverage (1.2-1.5Ã—)
â”œâ”€ Hedges: Minimal (5-10% in hedges)
â””â”€ Stop loss: Wider (can give stocks more room)

Current Status: [CHECK INDICATORS DAILY]

â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€

REGIME 2 - RISK-OFF (Crisis/Bear):
Indicators:
â”œâ”€ VIX-equivalent >30
â”œâ”€ Credit spreads blowing out (>400bp)
â”œâ”€ IDX down >15% from peak
â”œâ”€ Foreign flows: Heavy selling
â”œâ”€ Earnings misses widespread
â””â”€ Sentiment: Fear, capitulation

Strategy:
â”œâ”€ Equity allocation: 20-40% (defensive)
â”œâ”€ Sector preference: Defensives (consumer staples, utilities), gold
â”œâ”€ Leverage: NONE (risk-off)
â”œâ”€ Hedges: Maximum (30-50% in hedges, put options)
â””â”€ Stop loss: Tight (protect capital above all)

Current Status: [NOT IN REGIME 2 as of Jan 2026]

â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€

