Query: "gold price nickel price copper price [TODAY'S DATE]"
â”œâ”€ Sources: Kitco, LME, Bloomberg
â””â”€ Must be within 24 hours

EARNINGS/EVENTS (Priority 2):
Query: "[TICKER] earnings Indonesia [CURRENT QUARTER]"
Query: "[TICKER] news [CURRENT MONTH YEAR]"
â”œâ”€ Look for: Actual results, guidance, material events
â””â”€ Analyst reactions, estimate revisions

SECTOR CONTEXT (Priority 2):
